lx.test()

type: builtin_function_or_method

doc: Test the state of a toggle argument.

lx.throw()

type: builtin_function_or_method

doc: Raise a result code exception.

lx.trace()

type: builtin_function_or_method

doc: Toggle extra Event Log output for each lx function call.
